```

**Root Cause:** Prisma schema uses `@map()` directives to map camelCase TypeScript fields to snake_case database columns. The implementation correctly uses camelCase (matching Prisma's generated types), but the mock tests are testing against the database layer directly instead of the Prisma abstraction layer.

**Impact:** 
- All 8 test failures in classification-repository.test.ts
- Tests validate wrong interface (database instead of ORM)
